{"tid":1217594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想出個post 講下今次需要既醫療物資","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:33:42.000Z","uid":172093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2d6ea8caabfb43433447236124760a00ccb370","tid":1217594,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:30:01.000Z","msg":"當然 因為我本身對急救唔熟<br />\n都係朋友介紹我先知 所以可能有甩漏<br />\n主要希望大家唔好再有入錯野機會<br />\n1. 生理鹽水 （最重要）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhD9Xc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhD9Xc8.png&h=70a86ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imC3hdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimC3hdo.png&h=7f7618a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通常呢d都比較常見 基本藥房或者醫療野鋪都有<br />\n你同佢講 佢會俾到你<br />\n但好似市面上可能開始少 但下面呢隻洗con水都係一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTQ4L8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTQ4L8y.png&h=770cb76b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為生理鹽水好有用 所以重之中重<br />\n你中胡椒噴霧或催淚彈 全部靠佢洗眼<br />\n而且可以洗傷口 直頭家居旅行 殺人滅口 必備良藥<br />\n<br />\n2. 𠱼喘藥 （有冇巴打有推薦 我買開下面呢隻）<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScS3hgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScS3hgG.png&h=e37722ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於近矩離 中左催淚彈好易引起呼吸困難<br />\n加上宜家犬隻 經常性9扔催淚彈<br />\n所以好需要有哮喘藥係物資站<br />\n<br />\n3. Johnson baby shampoo(不澀眼配方）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7OJ1LB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7OJ1LB.png&h=8776b0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻如果以1份shampoo10份水既話<br />\n可以係眼睛中左胡椒噴霧既時候洗眼<br />\n可以洗走油份 令對眼舒服<br />\n<br />\n4.廚房紙<br />\n周街都有唔出相<br />\n中左胡椒噴霧既時候<br />\n可以用紙慢慢印返走d噴霧<br />\n一張紙處理完一部份 就用新la<br />\n如果用水冲反而沖唔走<br />\n<br />\n呢四種都係比較重要急救物資<br />\n當然 大膠布 繃帶呢d正常急求易需求都大<br />\n不過太易買 所以唔特別講<br />\n<br />\nBtw 其實奶唔太建議買<br />\n因為唔可以放太耐 同時洗眼容易入細菌<br />\n<br />\n仲有眼中左胡椒噴霧<br />\n唔好第一時間用水洗眼 <br />\n胡椒噴霧的殺傷成分是辣椒素<br />\n此化學物質不溶於水<br />\n所以可能洗唔甩不得止<br />\n沖返d野入去<br />\n<br />\nBtw 可能有好多甩漏<br />\n希望巴打補充再fact check先廣傳<br />\n等大家可以做好後勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1927f6072e20b288e633c3aab57cddc9f52442","tid":1217594,"uid":187825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcXZAjb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcXZAjb.png&h=98da57bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十二蚊店冰袋點睇"},{"pid":"bbbd65c0f7d9d360a33511ceccc0b60bc04894dd","tid":1217594,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"大水桶, 大量既水"},{"pid":"05170465d3c5ab3616c7ea72f8ffb4d8120aa768","tid":1217594,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c1927f6072e20b288e633c3aab57cddc9f52442","tid":1217594,"uid":187825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcXZAjb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcXZAjb.png&h=98da57bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十二蚊店冰袋點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:54:57.000Z","msg":"呢個可以加 但小林退熱貼有冇冰敷作用<br />\n好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b72af5ca2ead11ceacbdff6dd184dc80978124","tid":1217594,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}